  "prompt": "What is the AT&T wireless voicemail number?",
  "response": "To access your AT&T wireless voicemail, you typically dial your own phone number. If you want to set up or check your voicemail, you can dial **1** or press and hold the **1** key on your mobile phone. If you're looking for a specific voicemail service number, AT&T voicemail is usually set up to be accessed directly from your device. If you encounter issues, you may want to check the AT&T website or customer service for updated information.",
